name: CryptoNekos 01: Manekiss Neko
description:
Maneki Neko is a popular Japanese sculpture that brings luck, money and clients to its owner.

CryptoNekos is a syncretism combining the ancient Asian icon, with series of characters from Western pop culture.

In the NFTS world we are all looking for a piece of art that will attract money, and who better than the great Maneki Neko to do the job?

The sculpture in this animation is call ManeKiss Neko. It's a tribute to the rock band Kiss for their great music, but also for one of the comics that inspired me most when I was younger: Kiss Psycho Circus (I still keep it in the library of my studio!!).
​
This CryptoNeko will attract crypto, rhythm and rock to your life!
